爆打長小小先多反小小解釋，話上一手無跟自己無錯咁，咁你接手左之後點解都係咁呢請問？而且比個12位號既tracking number有咁難？<br />\n繼續問繼續無視，好啦，感謝你過左成個星期咁滯終於比到咁難先check到既number比我。尋日一收到秒check，無相關信息。。。。秒inbox，繼續無視，尋晚訓前check 多次，都係無相關信息。<br />\n到今朝，神奇既事發生了！有相關信息啦！係今朝19/4 08:07已取快件呀！咦，如果我無眼盲應該13號01:38AM 話已收走喔，難怪個12位數字咁難check一直比唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家，dm前要諗清楚呀<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/09w0mBj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09w0mBj.png&h=eef724e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5QHzVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD5QHzVN.png&h=7d0189ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RNp9eVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRNp9eVN.png&h=d4d1fd97&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aHEk52t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaHEk52t.png&h=a34d7f81&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LxOh8fO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxOh8fO.png&h=af98c0ac&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NoExcHu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNoExcHu.png&h=dc89e312&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2otJ3Pa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2otJ3Pa.png&h=b564103c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDVTGAQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDVTGAQ.jpg&h=d9cde95a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVEhoPb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVEhoPb.png&h=710bb37d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5FPZnw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5FPZnw.png&h=cff2f6c0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGQgEnx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2